14:["$","article",null,{"className":"pt-36 pb-32 px-6","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"max-w-2xl mx-auto","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"flex items-center gap-3 mb-8","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"pill-tag text-xs font-semibold px-3 py-1 rounded-full","children":"eBay SEO"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"text-xs","style":{"color":"#404060"},"children":"April 2025 · 6 min read"}]]}],["$","h1",null,{"className":"font-black leading-tight mb-6","style":{"fontSize":"clamp(30px, 4.5vw, 46px)","lineHeight":1.15},"children":"eBay SEO: How to Rank Higher and Sell More"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-lg mb-12 leading-relaxed","style":{"color":"#8080a0"},"children":"eBay's search engine — called Cassini — is fundamentally different from Etsy's. Understanding how it works is the single biggest lever you have for increasing visibility without spending a dollar on promoted listings."}],["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"How Cassini Ranks Listings"}],["$","p",null,{"children":["Cassini's primary goal is to show buyers the listings most likely to result in a completed transaction. It weighs three main signals: ",["$","strong",null,{"children":"relevancy"}]," (does this listing match the query?), ",["$","strong",null,{"children":"seller performance"}]," (does this seller reliably complete transactions?), and ",["$","strong",null,{"children":"listing completeness"}]," (does this listing have all the data Cassini needs to categorize and match it?)."]}],["$","p",null,{"children":["Unlike Etsy, eBay doesn't use freeform tags. Instead, it relies heavily on your ",["$","strong",null,{"children":"title"}],", ",["$","strong",null,{"children":"item specifics"}],", and ",["$","strong",null,{"children":"category"}]," to understand what you're selling. If any of those three elements are weak or missing, Cassini can't rank you effectively — no matter how good your price or photos are."]}],["$","h2",null,{"children":"1. Optimize Your Title for 80 Characters"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"eBay titles are capped at 80 characters. Every character counts. Cassini reads your title as a series of keyword phrases, so word placement and word choice directly determine which searches you appear in."}],["$","p",null,{"children":["$","strong",null,{"children":"What to include in your eBay title:"}]}],["$","ul",null,{"children":[["$","li",null,{"children":"Brand name (if relevant and searchable)"}],["$","li",null,{"children":"Model number or specific product identifier"}],["$","li",null,{"children":"Key attributes: color, size, material, condition"}],["$","li",null,{"children":"What it is — the category-level noun (mug, watch, sneaker, camera)"}],["$","li",null,{"children":"Buyer-intent modifiers: \"vintage,\" \"rare,\" \"new sealed,\" \"lot of 3\""}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"key-point","children":["$","p",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"Never waste title characters"}]," on words like \"look,\" \"nice,\" \"wow,\" \"awesome,\" \"L@@K,\" or exclamation marks. Cassini ignores them. Buyers don't search for them. They're pure noise."]}]}],["$","p",null,{"children":["A good framework: ",["$","em",null,{"children":"[Brand] [Model/Identifier] [Key Attribute] [Category Noun] [Condition/Modifier]."}]," For example: \"Nike Air Force 1 Low White Size 10 Men's Sneaker New In Box\" hits every major search signal a buyer looking for that shoe would use."]}],["$","h2",null,{"children":"2. Item Specifics Are Not Optional"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"This is where most eBay sellers lose the most rank. Item specifics are the structured data fields eBay provides for each category — things like brand, color, size, material, style, model, and country of manufacture. Many sellers fill in two or three and leave the rest blank."}],["$","p",null,{"children":["Cassini explicitly uses item specifics to match listings to filtered searches. When a buyer narrows results by brand, color, or size — which most serious buyers do — listings without those specifics are ","$L18",". You don't rank lower; you disappear."]}],"$L19","$L1a","$L1b","$L1c","$L1d","$L1e","$L1f","$L20","$L21","$L22","$L23","$L24","$L25","$L26","$L27","$L28"]}],"$L29"]}]}]
